{
  "stem": "5551.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not finish the story there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went out in that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] ever-smaller--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish-- Jewish neighborhoods that was left of the ghetto in Gorlice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And soon thereafter, all the young and vigorous people were loaded into cattle cars-- and that is-- was another experience-- and shipped to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, a very small contingent of Jewish people remained in town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were the ones that were highly positioned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And considered-- yes, they remained in town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother and my mother remained in town because they were [? both ?] working in the general hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we actually thought that they could escape this murderous orgy that was unleashed upon us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were taken away, along with the rest of the people, except for this small contingent of Jews that were higher positioned.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were packed into cattle cars, 100 men in a-- in a car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- the Germans offered no provisions, but we had some food stuff with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were no provisions for hygiene or toilet service.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just one corner was made for bowel function.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as far as urination or so, it was done through the cracks of the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] It was a horrifying experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Along the road, there were such who succumbed to the heat, exhaustion, hunger.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- they were simply made into mattresses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We-- we were resting our head on their bodies.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the trip-- even though it is a very short trip from Gorlice to Plaszow, it took, to the best of my recollections, three days, because the human cargo had two things-- it was transported in a sort of clandestine manner, not to make too much noise with it, and it had a low priority.",
      "word_count": 55
    }
  ],
